<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>SGT market</title>
    <link
      href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      type="text/css"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.css"
    />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a766c546f2.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-7VPbUDkoPSGFnVtYi0QogXtr74QeVeeIs99Qfg5YCF+TidwNdjvaKZX19NZ/e6oz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <style>
      .product-wrapper {
        width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .product-wrapper2 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .product-photo {
        width: 666px;
        height: 417px;

        background: #eeeeee;
      }

      .product-wrapper3 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 50px;
      }

      .product-wrapper4 {
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 50px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-left: 30px;
      }

      .product-wrapper4-2 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .product-wrapper5 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 50px;
        margin-top: 25px;
        margin-left: 30px;
        flex-direction: row;
        gap: 500px;
      }

      .product-wrapper6 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 50px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-left: 30px;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .profile-photo {
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        background-color: #eeeeee;
        border-radius: 100px;
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-right: 15px;
      }

      .user-nick {
        font-size: medium;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .user-address {
        font-size: small;
      }

      .hr-2 {
        margin-top: 20px;
        height: 0.1px;
        width: 680px;
        border: 0 none;
        color: #ccc;
        background-color: #ccc;
      }

      .product-name {
        font-size: medium;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .product-category,
      .product-upload-time {
        font-size: small;
      }

      .product-explanation {
        line-height: 30px;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
        color: rgb(77, 77, 77);
      }

      .price {
        font-size: medium;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .product-price {
        width: 100px;
        height: 30px;
        background-color: #ffe4bc;
        border-radius: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding-top: 10px;
      }

      .another-photo1,
      .another-photo2 {
        width: 300px;
        height: 210px;
        background: #eeeeee;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .another-product1,
      .another-product2 {
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .category-another-first,
      .category-another-second {
        line-height: 30px;
      }

      .category-another {
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-left: 30px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-left: 50px;
      }

      .chat-1 {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 30px;
        border: none;
        background-color: #eb8d00;
        color: white;
        font-weight: 900;
        right: 90px;
        outline: 0px;
        width: 100px;
        height: 40px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 20px;
        opacity: 0.8;
        z-index: 999;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%-include("navbar.ejs")%>
    <div class="product-wrapper">
      <div class="product-wrapper2">
        <div class="left-arrow">
          <i
            class="fa-solid fa-angle-left fa-2xl"
            style="margin-right: 20px"
          ></i>
        </div>
        <div class="product-photo"></div>
        <div class="right-arrow">
          <i
            class="fa-solid fa-angle-right fa-2xl"
            style="margin-left: 20px"
          ></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="product-wrapper3">
        <div class="profile-photo"></div>
        <div class="user-nick-add">
          <div class="user-nick">이름1</div>
          <div class="user-address">서울시 마포구 염리동</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="hr-2" />
      <div class="product-wrapper4">
        <div class="product-name">애플워치SE 미개봉 새제품</div>
        <div class="product-wrapper4-2">
          <div class="product-category">가전/생활용품</div>
          <span> • </span>
          <div class="product-upload-time">12시간 전</div>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="product-explanation">
          안녕하세요 <br />
          상품 설명 어쩌고 저쩌고 주절주절 어쩌고 저저고<br />
          사고싶은사람연락해라 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ <br />
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="hr-2" />
      <div class="product-wrapper5">
        <div class="price">가격</div>
        <div class="product-price">250,000<span>원</span></div>
      </div>
      <hr class="hr-2" />
      <div class="category-another">이 카테고리의 다른 상품</div>
      <div class="product-wrapper6">
        <div class="category-another-first">
          <div class="another-photo1"></div>
          <div class="another-product1">갤럭시 워치 5</div>
          <div class="another-price1">7,000원</div>
        </div>
        <div class="category-another-second">
          <div class="another-photo2"></div>
          <div class="another-product2">에어팟 프로 2세대</div>
          <div class="another-price2">17,000원</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <div>
      <button id="chat-1" class="chat-1" type="button" onclick="">
        채팅하기
      </button>
    </div>
    <%-include("footer.ejs")%>
  </body>
</html>
